@aabell77... there should be a .dll file installed in the default VST folder...
If you use any Steinberg product.. it should be inside it... If you can't see the VST listed in the host.. then find out the folder in which the .dll file is installed & add that to the VST directory manually...n your host should scan it out... Then it should work :)
Hope this helps :)
